These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, australian
2 different pets are kept: hamster, fish
House: colonial, townhouse
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, chess
1. the thai is on the far right##1
2. the colonial house is on the right of the person playing chess##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Nationality       | australian       | thai |
| Pet         | fish | hamster  |
| House       | townhouse    | colonial    |
| Game   | chess       | mah-jongg      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
House: victorian, townhouse
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, australian
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, boat
2 different pets are kept: mouse, pony
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the russian is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| House      | townhouse     | victorian |
| Nationality           | russian | australian      |
| Transport   | boat  | quad-bike      |
| Pet         | mouse | pony     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, marigold
2 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, manager
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, skydiving
1. the manager is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person who growsaconite is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Flower      | aconite | marigold  |
| Game          | backgammon    | scrabble   |
| Job   | manager  | security-guard   |
| Hobby     | skydiving     | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, aristoff
House: farmhouse, futuristic
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, january
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy
1. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Cigar      | swisher       | aristoff |
| House          | futuristic         | farmhouse    |
| Birthday           | january | august    |
| Flower   | lily           | daisy   |

