1. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Movie-Genre         | comedy | action   |
| House   | craftsman | cottage       |
| Cigar         | vegafina   | baccarat |
| Game     | monopoly    | scrabble     |

