2. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| Hobby          | drawing | traveling  |
| Beverage   | tea   | water     |
| Game         | go  | poker |
| City     | new-york       | boston    |

