.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, indonesian
House: modern, futuristic
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, lily
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, magic-tricks
1. the italian is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the italian is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who growsrose is the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Nationality           | indonesian | italian     |
| House   | modern          | futuristic |
| Flower           | rose          | lily    |
| Hobby     | magic-tricks            | woodworking       |

 